{"id":76005,"date":"2020-02-05T11:52:52","date_gmt":"2020-02-05T01:52:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/?p=76005"},"modified":"2021-10-14T10:08:50","modified_gmt":"2021-10-14T00:08:50","slug":"vetassess-professional-occupations","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/vetassess-professional-occupations\/","title":{"rendered":"VETASSESS Professional Occupations Groups"},"content":{"rendered":"[vc_row type=&#8221;in_container&#8221; full_screen_row_position=&#8221;middle&#8221; column_margin=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_tablet=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_phone=&#8221;default&#8221; scene_position=&#8221;center&#8221; text_color=&#8221;dark&#8221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221; row_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; row_border_radius_applies=&#8221;bg&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; shape_divider_position=&#8221;bottom&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221;][vc_column column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/1&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#8221;default&#8221; tablet_text_alignment=&#8221;default&#8221; phone_text_alignment=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; column_border_width=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][vc_column_text]Anzscosearch introduces new information to help users identify key information regarding <strong>VETASSESS assessment criteria<\/strong> in relation to General Professional occupations.<\/p>\n<p>VETASSESS classifies its General Professional occupations into groups A, B, C, D, E and F according to differences in educational and\/or employment criteria and the Indicative Skill level provided in the ANZSCO catalogue.<\/p>\n<p>This new information included in Anzscosearch helps users to quickly:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Identify if a selected occupation is classified under Group A, B, C, D, E or F.<\/li>\n<li>Access critical <a href=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/skills-assessment\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Skills Assessment<\/a> Criteria instantly.<\/li>\n<li>Access the VETASSESS list of general professional occupations in one-click.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_76026\" style=\"width: 1177px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-76026\" class=\"box-shadow-wide wp-image-76026 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/vetassess-group.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1167\" height=\"305\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/vetassess-group.jpg 1167w, https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/vetassess-group-300x78.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/vetassess-group-1024x268.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/vetassess-group-768x201.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1167px) 100vw, 1167px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-76026\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">VETASSESS Professional Occupation Group<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_76027\" style=\"width: 1237px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-76027\" class=\"box-shadow-wide wp-image-76027 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/vetassess-group-info.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1227\" height=\"922\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/vetassess-group-info.jpg 1227w, https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/vetassess-group-info-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/vetassess-group-info-1024x769.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/vetassess-group-info-768x577.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1227px) 100vw, 1227px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-76027\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">VETASSESS Professional Occupation Group Info<\/p><\/div>\n<p>The below is a summary of qualifications and employment requirements included in each Group:<\/p>\n<h3><strong>Group A \u2013 Skills Assessment criteria<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Qualification(s) assessed at Australian Bachelor degree or higher degree with a highly relevant field of study and at least one year of post-qualification highly relevant employment at an appropriate skill level in the last five years.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>Group B \u2013 Skills Assessment criteria<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qualification(s) assessed at AQF Bachelor degree or higher degree with a highly relevant field of study and at least one year of post-qualification highly relevant employment at an appropriate skill level in the last five years; OR<\/li>\n<li>Qualification(s) assessed at AQF Bachelor degree or higher degree with an additional qualification at least Australian Qualifications Framework (AQF) Diploma level in a highly relevant field of study and at least two years of post-qualification highly relevant employment at an appropriate skill level in the last five years; OR<\/li>\n<li>Qualification(s) assessed at AQF Bachelor degree or higher degree without a highly relevant field of study and at least three years of post-qualification highly relevant employment at an appropriate skill level in the last five years;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Additionally, <strong>pre-qualification employment<\/strong> may be considered for skills assessment purposes if the occupation is under this group being employment requirements as follows:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>five years of relevant employment required in addition to at least one year of highly relevant employment performed at the required skill level in the last 5 years before applying<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><strong>Group C \u2013 Skills Assessment criteria<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qualification(s) assessed at least AQF Diploma level with a highly relevant field of study and at least one year of post-qualification highly relevant employment at an appropriate skill level in the last five years; OR<\/li>\n<li>Qualification(s) assessed at least AQF Diploma level with an additional qualification at least AQF Certificate IV in a highly relevant field of study and at least one year of post-qualification highly relevant employment at an appropriate skill level in the last five years; OR<\/li>\n<li>Qualification(s) assessed at least AQF Diploma level without a highly relevant field of study and at least two years of post-qualification highly relevant employment at an appropriate skill level in the last five years;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Additionally, <strong>pre-qualification employment<\/strong> may be considered for skills assessment purposes if the occupation is under this group being employment requirements as follows:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>three years of relevant employment required in addition to at least one year of highly relevant employment performed at the required skill level in the last 5 years before applying.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><strong>Group D \u2013 Skills Assessment criteria<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qualification(s) assessed at AQF Certificate IV with a highly relevant field of study and at least one year of post-qualification highly relevant employment at an appropriate skill level in the last five years; OR<\/li>\n<li>Qualification(s) assessed at AQF Certificate IV without a highly relevant field of study and at least two years of post-qualification highly relevant employment at an appropriate skill level in the last five years; OR<\/li>\n<li>Qualification(s) assessed at AQF Certificate III with a highly relevant field of study and at least three years of post-qualification highly relevant employment at an appropriate skill level in the last five years;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Additionally, <strong>pre-qualification employment<\/strong> may be considered for skills assessment purposes if the occupation is under this group being employment requirements as follows:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>three years of relevant employment required in addition to at least one year of highly relevant employment performed at the required skill level in the last 5 years before applying.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><strong>Group E \u2013 Skills Assessment criteria<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qualification(s) assessed at AQF Diploma level with a highly relevant field of study and at least one year of post-qualification highly relevant employment at an appropriate skill level in the last five years.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><strong>Group F \u2013 Skills Assessment criteria<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qualification\/s assessed at least AQF Certificate II with a highly relevant field of study and at least one year of post-qualification highly relevant employment at an appropriate skill level in the last five years; OR<\/li>\n<li>Qualification\/s assessed at least AQF Certificate II without a highly relevant field of study and at least two years of post-qualification highly relevant employment at an appropriate skill level in the last five years;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><em>Source<\/em>: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.vetassess.com.au\/skills-assessment-for-migration\/professional-occupations\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">VETASSESS &#8211; Skills Assessment for Professional Occupations<\/a>[\/vc_column_text][divider line_type=&#8221;No Line&#8221; custom_height=&#8221;20&#8243;][nectar_global_section id=&#8221;109315&#8243;][\/vc_column][\